
1  

Kerai Amasia loka ikar akaisaarei ka lukany egeuni airum; kirumak ikar akaisaarei ka lukanykaoŋon koYerusalem: ekiror loka totoke kerai Yekoadan naka Yerusalem. 
2  

Kiswama nuejok kakonyen nuka Ejakait, konye mere keketau kere. 
3  

Kosodi kanen, nakitieasere akejakanut kamake, koar ikekejaanakinak luapotu koarata papake. 
4  

Konye mam abu koar ikecedwe, konye kiswama kwape ejaatar nuiwadikatai oitabo loka ikisila luka Musa, kwape kicorakinia EJAKAIT ebe, Mam lukapapa etwakikinete idwekec, karaida idwe atwakikin lukapapakec; konye etwanikini ŋinituŋanan akeronis.


5  

Bobo da kotukok Amasia Yuda, kitemonok kes kwape ajaatar ikekia luka lukapapakec, ikapolok luka ilukumin ka ikapolok luka akwat, Yuda kere ka Benyamin: kimara kes ageuni kaluka ikar akaisaarei ka adepar, kodum kes imwaasi ituŋa ilukumin akwat auni lueseunitai, luepedorete alosit ojie, luejenete aitwasam akwara ka ebuku. 
6  Kiboleoto ŋesi kituŋa ilukumin akwatat lukirigin luetitiŋ koIsirael atalatan akwatat nuka epuesa. 
7  

Konye kobu etuŋanan loka Edeke mama ejai, kotema atiar, “Wu ekabaka, kinyek ajore naka Isirael aupar kajo; naarai mam EJAKAIT ejai kaIsirael, kes idwe kere luka Epuraim. 
8  

Konye arai ilosi; kiswama katitiŋ, kogogoŋor kojie; kibirori Edeke jo kakonyen nuka lukasurupo; naarai ejai Edeke apedor aiŋarakin, ka aibiror.” 
9  

Kotema Amasia etuŋanan loka Edeke atiar, “Konye kikwaikini do ai nuka atalatan akwatat nuainak ajore naka Isirael?” Koboŋok etuŋanan loka Edeke ebe, “Epedori Edeke ainakin jo nuitelekarito ŋun.” 
10  Kosodi Amasia agitar kes, ajore naabuni mamake koEpuraim, aboŋor ore: ŋes kinepunia anyunyurakec noi aluikin Yuda, koboŋosi ore kanyunyura naepol. 
11  

Kotitiŋior Amasia, kiŋarenik iketuŋa, kolot Aditot naka Abalaŋ, kodany ilukumin itomon kodwe luka Seir. 
12  Kiioreutu idwe luka Yuda ice ilukumin itomon ejarete, koyaut kes kuju moru, kocakasi kes kokuju moru, kobilibiliunos. 
13  Konye ituŋa luka erioŋet loabu Amasia kinyaka, kinyeis aupar kaŋes ojie, kibirokinos ireria luka Yuda, anyoun koSamaria kiton Bet-koron, kodany ilukumin iuni kakesi, koyaŋaasi luŋatuna luipu.


14  

Kosodi kanen, kedau Amasia aboŋun kajar Idomein, koyau idekesio luka idwe luka Seir, kosipok kes araun idekesioke, kokukonokin kes, kisupuruikin kes lueur maa. 
15  

Ŋes kinepunia anyunyura naka EJAKAIT aluikin Amasia, kijukak ŋes enabi, loatemari ŋes atiar, “Kanukinyo imoiaa ijo idekesio luka ituŋa, lumam apotu kitajarata ikecetuŋa kakanikon?” 
16  

Kosodi kanen, kineras kaŋes, kotema ekabaka ŋes atiar, “Kidakakinit kereka isio jo araun lokaurianet naka ekabaka? Kinyek; kanukinyo tikiinomere?” Kosodi enabi ainyein, kotema atiar, “Ajeni ebe elosikinit Edeke amudiar jo, naarai iswama ŋun, komam iirari akainerun.”


17  

Kosodi Amasia ekabaka loka Yuda ainerun, kijuka da mama ejai Yoas okoku loka Yekoakas okoku loka Yeku, ekabaka loka Isirael ebe, “Bia, kaanyunos kakonye.” 
18  Kijuka Yoas ekabaka loka Isirael mama ejai Amasia ekabaka loka Yuda, kobala ebe, “Abu ekenep loajai Lebanon kijukak eres loajai Lebanon, ebe, Kokorak akokukon okokuka komany: kitoro etiaŋ loka ais loajai Lebanon, kicakacak ekenep. 
19  

Ibala ijo ebe, ‘Koany, adany Edom’; iturokina etaukon ailabilab: kopaik ore; kanukinyo ilomaria ijo akiro numere nukon ka atwaniar, kibirori ijo, ka Yuda da kajo?”


20  

Konye koŋer Amasia akiirar; naarai kerai akirot naka Edeke, tetere ijaikini kes akan naka lukasurupokec, naarai amoata idekesio luka Edom. 
21  Kolot do Yoas ekabaka loka Isirael; koanyunos kakonye, ŋesi ka Amasia ekabaka loka Yuda koBet-Semes, loarai loka Yuda. 
22  Kireŋeai Yuda kakonyen nuka Isirael; koker, ŋinituŋanan owemake. 
23  

Kikam Yoas ekabaka loka Isirael Amasia ekabaka loka Yuda, okoku loka Yoas, okoku loka Yekoakas, kolset-semes, koyau ŋes Yerusalem, kotiyatiya arwatat naka Yerusalem anyoun korute loka Epuraim kiton orute loka agor, ikubitin akwat aoŋon. 
24  Koŋata esabu ka epuesa kere, ka iboro kere luadumunio koObededom togo loka Edeke, ka iboro luka akais nuipu lukotogo loka ekabaka, ka lukititiŋa da, koboŋo Samaria.


25  

Kobut Amasia okoku loka Yoas ekabaka loka Yuda ikar itomon ka lukany akaulo katwanare naka Yoas okoku loka Yekoakas ekabaka loka Isirael. 
26  Aswamisio ace nuka Amasia, nusodit ka nukawasia, koany, mam kereka iwadikatai oitabo loka ikabakan luka Yuda ka Isirael? 
27  Agear kapaarasia nuebelokinor Amasia anyoun katupit EJAKAIT, kinerut asurokin ŋes koYerusalem; koker Lakis; konye kijukasi atupakin ŋes Lakis, koarakinai ŋina. 
28  

Koyaunai ŋes kobalasin, kidaikis nepepe kalukapapaake ore loka Yuda.

